meanings.definition: Not having a title or name.
meanings.sent1: The book had an untitled cover.
meanings.sent2: She found an untitled document on her desk.
meanings.sent3: The untitled painting confused everyone at the art show.
meanings.sent4: His untitled status made him feel invisible in the group.
meanings.sent5: The untitled song played softly in the background.

meanings.definition: A work of art that does not have a title.
meanings.sent1: The artist displayed an untitled sculpture in the gallery.
meanings.sent2: I purchased an untitled photograph from the exhibition.
meanings.sent3: The untitled drawing sparked a debate among the critics.
meanings.sent4: Her untitled masterpiece left viewers in awe.
meanings.sent5: The untitled artwork captured the essence of nature beautifully.
